I think this rooms a bit dead unfortunately but if you need any help just ask.

Hi all, I've re-purposed an old laptop as a chromebook for doing FCC so I'll be online most evenings if you want a chat or want to ask some questions, can't say I'll be too helpful until I get further
Hi @all, so I've started this again from scratch, I'll be around most days if anyone fancies a chat!
hey guys, what number project are you up to, I'm at 223 which isn't bad to say I only started it on Friday Night , Finding it quite fun now its getting a bit tougher.
Hi @MattBacon89 finding time is something I'm struggling with at the moment, tonight is the first time back on in 2 weeks. I'll keep an eye on this forum

Hi @StephenM1 nothing on the radar yet, two reasons. 1) finding the time with work is proving to be completely impossible. 2) I wanted to get a little deeper into FCC before organising something. I'm getting back on the FCC train now so hopefully I'll have something to share in the next few months. In the mean time there is no reason you couldn't organise something through facebook, we have a large community now I'm sure people would be up for it
Hello, just joined codecamp and wondered if a meetup was on the horizon?
